Package: prqlr
Title: R Bindings for the 'prqlc' Rust Library
Description:
    Provides a function to convert 'PRQL' strings to 'SQL' strings.
    Combined with other R functions that take 'SQL' as an argument,
    'PRQL' can be used on R.
Version: 0.8.1.9000
